Yes (0.03s cpu)
[eclipse 2]: 


[eclipse 3]: set_var_name(X, 'Myname'), set_var_name(Y, \"Myname\").

X = Myname#0
Y = Myname#1
Yes (0.00s cpu)
[eclipse 4]: set_var_name(X, 'Count'), writeln(X).
