L = [Start#0, Start#1, Start#2, Start#3, Start#4]
Yes (0.00s cpu)

% counter is backtrackable
[eclipse 11]: (set_var_name([X,Y], 'Name') ; set_var_name(Y, 'Name')), writeln(X-Y), fail.
